#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.115"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.115:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.115:0.2"
msgid "12. Kesivagga "
msgstr "12. With Kesi "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.115:0.3"
msgid "115. Ṭhānasutta "
msgstr "115. Things "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.115:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, ṭhānāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four things. "

msgctxt "an4.115:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><ol><li>
msgctxt "an4.115:1.3"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, ṭhānaṃ amanāpaṃ kātuṃ; "
msgstr "There is a thing that’s unpleasant to do, "

msgctxt "an4.115:1.4"
msgid "tañca kayiramānaṃ anatthāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "and doing it proves harmful. "

#. HTML: </li><li>
msgctxt "an4.115:1.5"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, ṭhānaṃ amanāpaṃ kātuṃ; "
msgstr "There is a thing that’s unpleasant to do, "

msgctxt "an4.115:1.6"
msgid "tañca kayiramānaṃ atthāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "but doing it proves beneficial. "

#. HTML: </li><li>
msgctxt "an4.115:1.7"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, ṭhānaṃ manāpaṃ kātuṃ; "
msgstr "There is a thing that’s pleasant to do, "

msgctxt "an4.115:1.8"
msgid "tañca kayiramānaṃ anatthāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "but doing it proves harmful. "

#. HTML: </li><li>
msgctxt "an4.115:1.9"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, ṭhānaṃ manāpaṃ kātuṃ; "
msgstr "There is a thing that’s pleasant to do, "

msgctxt "an4.115:1.10"
msgid "tañca kayiramānaṃ atthāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "and doing it proves beneficial. "

#. HTML: </li></ol><p>
#. REF: sc2
#. VAR: yamidaṃ → yadidaṃ (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "an4.115:2.1"
msgid "Tatra, bhikkhave, yamidaṃ ṭhānaṃ amanāpaṃ kātuṃ; "
msgstr "Take the thing that’s unpleasant to do, "

msgctxt "an4.115:2.2"
msgid "tañca kayiramānaṃ anatthāya saṃvattati—"
msgstr "and doing it proves harmful. "

#. VAR: maññati → paññāyati (?)
msgctxt "an4.115:2.3"
msgid "idaṃ, bhikkhave, ṭhānaṃ ubhayeneva na kattabbaṃ maññati. "
msgstr "This is regarded as a thing that shouldn’t be done on both grounds: "

#. VAR: Yampidaṃ → yadidaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an4.115:2.4"
msgid "Yampidaṃ ṭhānaṃ amanāpaṃ kātuṃ; "
msgstr "because it’s unpleasant, "

#. VAR: naṃ → taṃ (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.115:2.5"
msgid "imināpi naṃ na kattabbaṃ maññati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.115:2.6"
msgid "Yampidaṃ ṭhānaṃ kayiramānaṃ anatthāya saṃvattati; "
msgstr "and because doing it proves harmful. "

#. VAR: naṃ → taṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "an4.115:2.7"
msgid "imināpi naṃ na kattabbaṃ maññati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.115:2.8"
msgid "Idaṃ, bhikkhave, ṭhānaṃ ubhayeneva na kattabbaṃ maññati. "
msgstr "This is regarded as a thing that shouldn’t be done on both grounds. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.119, sc3
msgctxt "an4.115:3.1"
msgid "Tatra, bhikkhave, yamidaṃ ṭhānaṃ amanāpaṃ kātuṃ; "
msgstr "Next, take the thing that’s unpleasant to do, "

msgctxt "an4.115:3.2"
msgid "tañca kayiramānaṃ atthāya saṃvattati—"
msgstr "but doing it proves beneficial. "

msgctxt "an4.115:3.3"
msgid "imasmiṃ, bhikkhave, ṭhāne bālo ca paṇḍito ca veditabbo purisathāme purisavīriye purisaparakkame. "
msgstr "It is here that you can tell who is foolish and who is astute in regard to manly strength, energy, and vigor. "

msgctxt "an4.115:3.4"
msgid "Na, bhikkhave, bālo iti paṭisañcikkhati: "
msgstr "A fool doesn’t reflect: "

msgctxt "an4.115:3.5"
msgid "‘kiñcāpi kho idaṃ ṭhānaṃ amanāpaṃ kātuṃ; "
msgstr "‘Despite the fact that this thing is unpleasant to do, "

msgctxt "an4.115:3.6"
msgid "atha carahidaṃ ṭhānaṃ kayiramānaṃ atthāya saṃvattatī’ti. "
msgstr "doing it still proves beneficial.’ "

msgctxt "an4.115:3.7"
msgid "So taṃ ṭhānaṃ na karoti. "
msgstr "They don’t do that thing, "

msgctxt "an4.115:3.8"
msgid "Tassa taṃ ṭhānaṃ akayiramānaṃ anatthāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "so that proves harmful. "

msgctxt "an4.115:3.9"
msgid "Paṇḍito ca kho, bhikkhave, iti paṭisañcikkhati: "
msgstr "An astute person does reflect: "

msgctxt "an4.115:3.10"
msgid "‘kiñcāpi kho idaṃ ṭhānaṃ amanāpaṃ kātuṃ; "
msgstr "‘Despite the fact that this thing is unpleasant to do, "

msgctxt "an4.115:3.11"
msgid "atha carahidaṃ ṭhānaṃ kayiramānaṃ atthāya saṃvattatī’ti. "
msgstr "doing it still proves beneficial.’ "

msgctxt "an4.115:3.12"
msgid "So taṃ ṭhānaṃ karoti. "
msgstr "They do that thing, "

msgctxt "an4.115:3.13"
msgid "Tassa taṃ ṭhānaṃ kayiramānaṃ atthāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "so that proves beneficial. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
#. VAR: yamidaṃ → yadidaṃ (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an4.115:4.1"
msgid "Tatra, bhikkhave, yamidaṃ ṭhānaṃ manāpaṃ kātuṃ; "
msgstr "Next, take the thing that’s pleasant to do, "

msgctxt "an4.115:4.2"
msgid "tañca kayiramānaṃ anatthāya saṃvattati—"
msgstr "but doing it proves harmful. "

msgctxt "an4.115:4.3"
msgid "imasmimpi, bhikkhave, ṭhāne bālo ca paṇḍito ca veditabbo purisathāme purisavīriye purisaparakkame. "
msgstr "It is here that you can tell who is foolish and who is astute in regard to manly strength, energy, and vigor. "

msgctxt "an4.115:4.4"
msgid "Na, bhikkhave, bālo iti paṭisañcikkhati: "
msgstr "A fool doesn’t reflect: "

msgctxt "an4.115:4.5"
msgid "‘kiñcāpi kho idaṃ ṭhānaṃ manāpaṃ kātuṃ; "
msgstr "‘Despite the fact that this thing is pleasant to do, "

msgctxt "an4.115:4.6"
msgid "atha carahidaṃ ṭhānaṃ kayiramānaṃ anatthāya saṃvattatī’ti. "
msgstr "doing it still proves harmful.’ "

msgctxt "an4.115:4.7"
msgid "So taṃ ṭhānaṃ karoti. "
msgstr "They do that thing, "

msgctxt "an4.115:4.8"
msgid "Tassa taṃ ṭhānaṃ kayiramānaṃ anatthāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "and so that proves harmful. "

msgctxt "an4.115:4.9"
msgid "Paṇḍito ca kho, bhikkhave, iti paṭisañcikkhati: "
msgstr "An astute person does reflect: "

msgctxt "an4.115:4.10"
msgid "‘kiñcāpi kho idaṃ ṭhānaṃ manāpaṃ kātuṃ; "
msgstr "‘Despite the fact that this thing is pleasant to do, "

msgctxt "an4.115:4.11"
msgid "atha carahidaṃ ṭhānaṃ kayiramānaṃ anatthāya saṃvattatī’ti. "
msgstr "doing it still proves harmful.’ "

msgctxt "an4.115:4.12"
msgid "So taṃ ṭhānaṃ na karoti. "
msgstr "They don’t do that thing, "

msgctxt "an4.115:4.13"
msgid "Tassa taṃ ṭhānaṃ akayiramānaṃ atthāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "so that proves beneficial. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.115:5.1"
msgid "Tatra, bhikkhave, yamidaṃ ṭhānaṃ manāpaṃ kātuṃ, tañca kayiramānaṃ atthāya saṃvattati—"
msgstr "Next, take the thing that’s pleasant to do, and doing it proves beneficial. "

msgctxt "an4.115:5.2"
msgid "idaṃ, bhikkhave, ṭhānaṃ ubhayeneva kattabbaṃ maññati. "
msgstr "This is regarded as a thing that should be done on both grounds: "

msgctxt "an4.115:5.3"
msgid "Yampidaṃ ṭhānaṃ manāpaṃ kātuṃ, imināpi naṃ kattabbaṃ maññati; "
msgstr "because it’s pleasant, "

msgctxt "an4.115:5.4"
msgid "yampidaṃ ṭhānaṃ kayiramānaṃ atthāya saṃvattati, imināpi naṃ kattabbaṃ maññati. "
msgstr "and because doing it proves beneficial. "

msgctxt "an4.115:5.5"
msgid "Idaṃ, bhikkhave, ṭhānaṃ ubhayeneva kattabbaṃ maññati. "
msgstr "This is regarded as a thing that should be done on both grounds. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.115:5.6"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri ṭhānānī”ti. "
msgstr "These are the four things.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.115:5.7"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
